658
01:23:34,520 --> 01:23:39,640
...es verdad... casi lo
pude lograr con tu padre

659
01:23:40,040 --> 01:23:42,040
Vete al infierno...

660
01:23:45,920 --> 01:23:49,840
...que te mate sólo te
liberará de la culpa...

661
01:23:51,400 --> 01:23:53,400
...vámonos

662
01:24:05,600 --> 01:24:07,600
No te puede ir

663
01:24:07,640 --> 01:24:09,640
Ishmael

664
01:24:10,920 --> 01:24:12,640
No

665
01:24:12,720 --> 01:24:15,240
No, Queequeg... Queequeg...

666
01:24:16,120 --> 01:24:16,720
No...

667
01:24:16,840 --> 01:24:18,840
...no...

668
01:24:30,200 --> 01:24:32,200
Te voy a matar

669
01:25:22,400 --> 01:25:24,400
Rachel...

670
01:25:51,080 --> 01:25:55,120
